rComments: This prof really wants you to succeed and she is passionate about her work
Great teacher! Very passionate and fair!

The material taught is simple and easy to understand, you just have to attend her lectures. She gives very good feedback on assignments, you can tell that she cares a lot about her students' success. Projects are pretty simple, but can sometimes be a little long. She is also very accessible out of class and she answers every question clearly.
